kdl.prox.qgraph2.family
Class QueryGen

java.lang.Object
  kdl.prox.qgraph2.family.QueryGen

public class QueryGen
extends java.lang.Object

The actual class that generates a set of qgraph2 query (xml) files from a (xml) specification.

Receives the root Element of an xml query-family specification, and creates a list with all the possible query instances. Those instances are then accessible via getQueryInstances
